gr.interamerican.bo2.impl.open.job
Class JobCapableTransactionManager

java.lang.Object
  gr.interamerican.bo2.impl.open.job.JobCapableTransactionManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
TransactionManager
Direct Known Subclasses:
JdbcConnectionsTransactionManager, JtaTransactionManager
public abstract class JobCapableTransactionManager
extends Object
implements TransactionManager

Abstract base implementation of a TransactionManager that knows how to handle jobs.
Jobs are scheduled within a UOW. Users extending this class should

  • Submit any scheduled jobs by calling submitScheduledJobs() if the transaction commits successfully. After submitting, jobs are cleared by calling clearScheduledJobs().
  • Clear the scheduled jobs without submitting them in any other case.
